\par

\pard\f0\fs28  ({\b b}) Subsp. {\b antri-jovis} (Kümmerle) Brownsey & Jermy,{\i  Brit. Fern Gaz.}{\b  10}: 346 (1973) ({\i Biropteris antri-jovis} Kümmerle): Leaves not more than 20 cm, the margins indented. Sori extending to the indentations of the margin of the leaf. 2n = 72.{\i  Mountains of Kriti}. ({\i Palestine}.)
