\pard\f0\fs28 Subgen. {\b Phyllitopsis} (Reichstein) Jermy & Viane. Leaves simple to pinnatifid; lamina sparsely scaly; veins free or rarely anastomosing at the margins. Sorus single or paired on a vein; indusium present.
\par

